ADDR_BOUND = ids.ADDR_BOUND % PRIME
assert (2**250 < ADDR_BOUND <= 2**251) and (2 * 2**250 < PRIME) and (
        ADDR_BOUND * 2 > PRIME), \

ids.is_small = 1 if ids.addr < ADDR_BOUND else 0
